{
  "chapter": 30,
  "chapter_summary": "本章以\"快讯\"花玉临死前留下的\"只会一招\"四字为引，揭示裴珏仅从金童玉女处学会七招绝学中的一招。场景转至浪莽山庄，神手战飞设下赌局，以黄金诱使群豪押注裴珏与冷谷双木比斗的胜负。龙形八掌檀明率先以六千五百两汇丰银票参赌，其手下快马神刀龚清洋精明算账却遭战飞讥嘲断手，结下深仇。东方五兄弟紧随其后押注古玉相助。金鸡帮帮主向一啼更以九名锦衣死士的身体性命为奇异赌注，九人当众展示惊人神功——以八人之力将铁棍拉细切断，震慑全场。本章通过层层加码的赌局，展现各方势力对裴珏武功深浅的试探与暗中较量。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_tong_yu_nv",
      "speaker_name": "金童玉女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "总有一天，你会知道的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手战飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位怎地不快些饮酒，难道暗中在为‘裴大先生’担心么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手战飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "错了，错了，错了……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手战飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "裴大先生直到今日为止，在武林中的声名，或者不如冷谷双木的响亮，但各位且看裴大先生方才所显露的武功，哈哈——便是区区在下，也挡不住这么地三招！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手战飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若有谁不信裴大先生的武功，我战某要愿意和他博上一博。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手战飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "该死该死，小人无知，竟以这区区之数，来打扰各位的酒兴！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手战飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "该死的奴才，还不再去取一些来，作为各位英雄酒后消遣的财物。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手战飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "区区之物，不过聊博各位一笑而已！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_gong_qing_yang",
      "text": "清洋，过来！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_gong_qing_yang",
      "text": "清洋，你身上可曾带得有银子么？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手战飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "檀老镖头难道也有这般雅兴么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "不知战庄主是否俯允在下这局外人参与这精彩的游戏！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手战飞",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "自然，自然……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "如今金银之比率，可是以五易一么？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手战飞",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "正是，正是！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_qing_yang",
      "speaker_name": "快马神刀",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "战庄主面前的黄金，大约是每盘两百四十两，折合白银六千两整。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手战飞",
      "listener": "char_gong_qing_yang",
      "text": "龚镖头好厉害的眼力，好精明的算盘，纵然不作刀枪上的买卖……嘿嘿，嘿嘿，飞龙镖局的大掌柜，只怕非龚兄莫属了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_gong_qing_yang",
      "text": "战兄高见，确是不凡，身手残废的人，总要比头脑痴呆的人好得多，清洋，你正该谢谢战庄主的夸奖。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手战飞",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "岂敢，岂敢……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "这里是汇丰的银票，共是六千五百两，请战庄主过目。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手战飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不会错的，不会错的！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手战飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "除了檀老镖头有此雅兴外，还有哪位兄弟……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "speaker_name": "东方铁",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "小弟也正觉手痒得很。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手战飞",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "text": "东方大侠……哈哈，好极了，好极了！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "speaker_name": "东方铁",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "但小弟身边未带金银，只是以区区之物，聊以助兴罢了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手战飞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_yi_ti",
      "text": "向兄难道也有此雅兴么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yi_ti",
      "speaker_name": "金鸡",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "如此热闹的赌博，我向某人若不凑上一脚，岂非要终生遗憾！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yi_ti",
      "speaker_name": "金鸡",
      "listener": "char_ji_wei_jiu_xiong_di",
      "text": "你九人身体性命从何而来？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_wei_jiu_xiong_di",
      "speaker_name": "鸡尾九兄弟",
      "listener": "char_xiang_yi_ti",
      "text": "身属金鸡，命属金鸡，金鸡有令，百死无憾！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yi_ti",
      "speaker_name": "金鸡",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "今日我向一啼要与战庄主你一赌的，便是这九人的身体性命。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yi_ti",
      "speaker_name": "金鸡",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "战庄主仁义待人，一代之雄，手下想必多得是能为战庄主卖命的兄弟，只要随意选出九人来，也就是了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_ji_wei_jiu_xiong_di",
      "text": "人命关天，终非儿戏，你九人可是当真心甘情愿？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yi_ti",
      "speaker_name": "金鸡",
      "listener": "char_ji_wei_jiu_xiong_di",
      "text": "檀总镖头的话，你们难道没有听到么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_wei_jiu_xiong_di",
      "speaker_name": "鸡尾九兄弟",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "听到了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yi_ti",
      "speaker_name": "金鸡",
      "listener": "char_ji_wei_jiu_xiong_di",
      "text": "听到了怎不回答檀老镖头的话？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_wei_jiu_xiong_di",
      "speaker_name": "鸡尾九兄弟",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "君赐臣死，臣不敢不死，父令子亡，子不敢不亡，向大哥于我等恩情有如君父，是以我九人实是心甘情愿，万死不辞！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_xiang_yi_ti",
      "text": "向帮主请恕在下多事！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yi_ti",
      "speaker_name": "金鸡",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "战庄主是否在嫌我鸡尾九兄弟太过愚鲁呆笨，是以觉得这九条贱命，不值得与战庄主手下的济济长才相提并论？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手战飞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_yi_ti",
      "text": "向帮主言重了，但……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yi_ti",
      "speaker_name": "金鸡",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "如是这般，那么在下只有令我这鸡尾九兄弟在战庄主面前献一献丑了！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 283
    }
  ],
